net.rithms.test

Class RiotApiTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.rithms.test.RiotApiTest

  • public class RiotApiTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Runs all synchronous and asynchronous tests. You might need an api key with extended limits to run all the tests at once.

    For these tests to work, you need to insert your api key below in the variable apiKey.
